        "TileImage": "$($repository d131cc85-e73e-42e1-b200-eb1544dac5c5).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47. Today we have only one target, located in Morocco, specifically in Marrakesh. His name is Timmie Beavington, and he is an amateur chef. He participated in an amateur chef competition a few weeks ago, where he cheated and sabotaged other competitors to win. However, our client was one of the competitors, and his restaurant has gone bankrupt and the client has lost all his popularity due to the loss. If you don&apos;t kill Timmie in 15 minutes, he will flee and the mission will fail.",
